fix: make jieba-wasm lazy-loaded and external for build/CI compatibility

- tokenizer.ts: dynamic require() with graceful fallback (passthrough
  if jieba-wasm unavailable)
- package.json: add jieba-wasm to server dependencies + --external flag
  for bun build --compile (WASM modules can't be embedded)

